## Component Migration API - Overview

```English
Use the Component Migration APIs to migrate components, including segments, calculated metrics, and date ranges in Analytics to data views in Customer Journey Anaytics. You can also migrate dimensions and metrics to CJA data views if you have already mapped them with the Dimension Mapping APIs or the Metric Mapping APIs.
```

## Cloud API Use Cases (Python)

```python
import adobe_analytics_api_client
from adobe_analytics_api_client.rest import ApiException

# Configure API key authorization: Bearer
configuration = adobe_analytics_api_client.Configuration()
configuration.api_key['Bearer'] = 'YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN'
# Configure API key authorization: ApiKey
configuration.api_key['ApiKey'] = 'YOUR_API_KEY'

# create an instance of the API class
api_instance = adobe_analytics_api_client.CloudAccountsApi(adobe_analytics_api_client.ApiClient(configuration))

try:
    # Example: Get all cloud accounts
    api_response = api_instance.get_cloud_accounts()
    print(api_response)
except ApiException as e:
    print("Exception when calling CloudAccountsApi: %s\n" % e)
```

